Package: leninature
Title: Provides the works of Lenin in an analysis-ready format
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alice Circe", "Malone", ,"circemalone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains all of Lenin's works available on the 
    Marxists Internet Archive (marxists.org) in the form of a tidy data frame.
